               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18360201-name-373" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18360201-name-373" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360201-name-373" type="surname" value="BARLOW"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360201-name-373" type="given" value="ELIZABETH"></interp>ELIZABETH BARLOW</persName>
                  </hi>. I am single. This copper was taken from my dwelling-house, in Marylebone-lane—it was fixed in the back kitchen—I saw it safe on the morning of the 12th of January, and missed it about nine o'clock in the evening, when one of my lodgers met the prisoner going out with it—the prisoner lodged in my house about three weeks—he had not left—I understood he was a sadler.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
